# Keep the build context lean + never ship local secrets or test data into the image.
# The runtime needs src/ + package.json + the contract file (/health reads its version).
.git
.gitignore
node_modules
.env
.env.*
test
fixtures
spikes
docs
memory
.claude
.vscode
*.md
!package.json
# The contract file MUST ship — the service sources its version from it at boot (contractVersion.ts).
!contracts/quote-api-contract.md
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
